      |+ getProducts() : List<Product>|      
      `-------------------------------'      
                      |                      
          ,-----------------------.          
          |Product                |          
          |-----------------------|          
          |- name : String        |          
          |- quantity : int       |          
          |- pricePerUnit : double|          
          `-----------------------'          



